== Language Agreement

I am going to use the language mixed Hanzi (Kanji) and English in this note, and hoping both Chinese and Japanese readers can understand it. 

我發現 many 名詞 in 中國語 and 日本語 are 同一, but 文法 and 副詞 are 完全 different. So my 提案 is 借用 some 副詞 from 英語, then 中國人 and 日本人 can 互相交流 with 中學生 level 英語 and 漢字.
